            <h1>Installing on MAC OS X</h1>
            <p>The Embedthis ESP install distribution for Mac OSX is published as a an
            installable pkg file.</p>

            <a id="pkg"></a>
            <h2>Installing the PKG Image</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Double click on the PKG image.</li>
            </ol>

            <a id="removing"></a>
            <h2>Removing ESP</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Run a terminal and change directory to the installation directory for ESP. This is typically
                <em>/usr/lib/esp/latest</em></li>
                <li><p>Run the remove script in the install directory for ESP by typing:</p>
                    <code class="inverted">
sudo ./uninstall
</code>
                </li>
            </ol>
